Package fil.sr1

Contains the entry point related to the ServeurFtp project, the Main class. And all the packages linked to the proper functioning of ServeurFtp
Author:
Adrien Holvoet and Anthony Mendez
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Main
    Application entry point with 3 arguments : 1 - the path of the local repository of the FTP server (mandatory), 2 - the port number (mandatory), 3 - the number of users who can connect simultaneously, this number is 5 by default (optionnal)
